      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail reflects a legacy of fastidious ownership. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, offering the performance and aesthetic integrity of a new arrival. We invite the most discerning collectors to inspect this benchmark example.",
