    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been totally babied and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
