      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you\u2014it is stunning! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Honestly, it\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in absolutely flawless shape inside and out. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on this beauty. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
